---
// Colaboraciones.astro
---

<!-- Recent Works & Collaborations (Reformatted) -->
<section class="pt-8 pb-10" id="collab">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Carousel Area (Left) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-5 xl:col-span-5 3xl:col-span-7 w-[90%] md:w-full mx-auto bg-surface-container-low shadow-xl group relative carousel-container">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] max-h-[70vh] md:max-h-none">
                <div class="carousel-track h-full scroll-smooth">
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 1" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f1.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 2" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f2.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f3.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img alt="Drag Item 4" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-700" src="/img-col-car-1/f4.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Controls -->
                <button
                    class="absolute z-10 top-1/2 left-6 -translate-y-1/2 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-white/80   hover:scale-105 shadow-md rounded-full text-black/80 hover:text-black backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 opacity-0  group-hover:opacity-100 carousel-prev"
                    aria-label="Anterior">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_back_ios_new</span>
                </button>
                <button
                    class="absolute z-10 top-1/2 right-6 -translate-y-1/2 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-white/80   hover:scale-105 shadow-md rounded-full text-black/80 hover:text-black backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 opacity-0  group-hover:opacity-100 carousel-next"
                    aria-label="Siguiente">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_forward_ios</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text Area (Right) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-7 xl:col-span-7 3xl:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left gap-8 px-6 md:px-0 md:pr-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center md:items-start">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight font-light text-on-surface italic">Alei X Springfield</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed text-center md:text-justify">
                    Springfield y Alei, artista gallego, se unen en una colección de San Valentín que celebra el amor cotidiano. Inspirada en la idea de que el amor es como una flor, esta colaboración reivindica el cuidado diario, los pequeños gestos y la importancia de la constancia.
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed text-center md:text-justify">Una colección para San Valentín, y para el resto del año, porque querer es algo que pasa todos los días, y si es mucho, mejor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

